  "original_title": "177 \u0baa\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0ba3\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0ba8\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f 4 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd 6 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "4 arrested for robbing 177 pounds of gold jewelery 6 months later",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Four suspects were arrested yesterday (30), six months after the incident, for breaking into a gold jewelery pawn shop in Norwood and robbing them of 177 pounds worth of jewelery worth about 3 crore 15 lakhs.",
        "Three men and one woman living in the Norwood area have been arrested by officers of the Anti-Corruption Unit of Aton Police.",
        "On December 09, 2021, the shop was broken into and robbery and gold jewelery were stolen. A complaint was lodged with the police in this regard.",
        "Following this, a woman who had worked in the shop for about 10 years was arrested on suspicion and interrogated and her fingerprints were recorded.",
        "Police said that the fingerprints of the woman who was arrested and interrogated were the same as the fingerprints found in the recovered items.",
        "Following this the investigation hunt began. The masterminds were hastily arrested while they were being arranged to sell the stolen jewelery.",
        "A few more gold jewelery including 54 gold chains, 757 necklaces, 177 pendants, 18 bracelets, 1 gold necklace were looted."
      ],
